🎓 Student Registration Dashboard


📖 Overview

The **Student Registration Dashboard** is a front-end web application that helps manage student information efficiently. It allows users to add, edit, delete, and view student records using CRUD operations. The project demonstrates responsive web design, DOM manipulation, JavaScript validation, and dynamic table updates.

---

✨ Features

- 📊 Dashboard Overview
- ➕ Add Student
- ✏️ Edit Student Details
- 🗑️ Delete Student
- 📋 Display Student Records
- 🔍 Search Students
- 📱 Responsive Design
- ⚡ Client-side Validation
- 🎨 Modern User Interface

---

🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)

---

📂 Project Structure

```
Student-Registration-Dashboard/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
│── README.md
│── LICENSE
│── .gitignore
```

---

 📚 Modules

📊 Dashboard
   Displays an overview of the application and student statistics.

👨‍🎓 Student Management
   Add, edit, delete, and manage student information.

📋 Student Records
   Displays all registered students in a responsive table.

🔍 Search
   Quickly search students by ID or Name.

✏️ Edit Records
   Update student details instantly.

🗑️ Delete Records
   Remove unwanted student records safely.

---

🎯 Objectives

 - Develop a responsive web application.
 - Perform CRUD operations using JavaScript.
 - Practice DOM manipulation.
 - Create a clean and modern dashboard.
 - Improve front-end development skills.

---

🏗 System Architecture

```
User
   │
Web Browser
   │
HTML + CSS Interface
   │
JavaScript Application
   │
Student Data (Array)
   │
Dynamic Dashboard
```

---

🗄 Data Structure

Student Table

| Field | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Student ID | Unique ID |
| Name | Student Name |
| Email | Student Email |
| Course | Course Name |

