  End
```
✅ Conclusion

The **Student Registration Dashboard** is a responsive and user-friendly web application developed using **HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript**. It demonstrates the implementation of CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations, DOM manipulation, and responsive web design in a practical project. The application provides an efficient way to manage student records through a clean and interactive interface. This project serves as a strong foundation for learning front-end web development and can be extended with features such as Local Storage, database integration, user authentication, and cloud deployment in future versions.


